{
  "texts": [
    "The team then re ned these questions to include those most commonly asked by patients and parents in clinical contexts.",
    "To thoroughly evaluate the capabilities of LLM-Chatbots across a spectrum of topics, the questions were divided into 10 categories of disorders commonly associated with adolescent development stages: Attention De cit Disorder, Tic Disorder, Developmental Delay, Autism, Anxiety Disorder, Anorexia Nervosa, Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder, Sleep Disorders, Precocious Puberty, and Depression.",
    "The responses were elicited using ChatGPT-3.5 by OpenAI, Claude2 by Anthropic, and Bard by Google, during the period from October 22 to November 29, 2023.",
    "While ChatGPT-3.5 and Google Bard are available to the public at no cost, accessing Claude2 for extended text generation necessitates a subscription.",
    "With more parameters and computational capacity than ChatGPT-3.5, Claude2 is presumed to handle complex queries more effectively."
  ]
}